{"tid":1424431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<廣傳>8月13子時18區燒衣祭義士","createTime":"2019-08-06T15:52:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T12:32:02.000Z","uid":79589,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"dbaec6e5986f06686cf6e05e00f1dff399d46715","tid":1424431,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:52:29.000Z","msg":"嗚呼哀哉，嗚呼哀哉！<br />\n<br />\n義士為求公義，以死明志，但至今五大訴求無一達成，反遭極權軍政府強力打壓。<br />\n<br />\n義士泉下有知，必然無法安心，不能早登極樂！<br />\n<br />\n適逢鬼節將至，到時鬼門大開。深恐義士聞見訴求無應，遺留塵世，徘徊於警局之間，積怨成厲，為渡義士亡魂，昭告抗爭到底，現邀各區義士自行組織燒衣公祭！<br />\n<br />\n地點: 各地狗竇、金鐘太古廣場<br />\n<br />\n時間: 8月13日子時 (晚上11時起)<br />\n<br />\n物資: 化寶盤數個、符敕、香燭衣紙、水果雞蛋、大慈大悲咒聲帶、金銀衣紙等等<br />\n<br />\n嗚呼哀哉！嗚呼哀哉！"},{"pid":"8eadbf6c3a020deb30976632dbe0e6878ba3d90a","tid":1424431,"uid":269389,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:53:45.000Z","msg":"怨有頭 責有主<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f62954e00327ae9f6f12e82511a8d204ebbe806","tid":1424431,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:53:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e5bf5d94758eb11be0d4d3f9a549b6918819c84","tid":1424431,"uid":140022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:54:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0d1c2221de0102f4d98abe44a5b08e5b7572c438","tid":1424431,"uid":41901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:54:08.000Z","msg":"7月..."},{"pid":"7fe2aeffb4e9c261afa7099a82b62bdc115b2045","tid":1424431,"uid":269389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8eadbf6c3a020deb30976632dbe0e6878ba3d90a","tid":1424431,"uid":269389,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:53:45.000Z","msg":"怨有頭 責有主<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:54:31.000Z","msg":"怨有頭 債有怨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=